title: Kimi to wa 2-do to Kiss Dekinai
original_name: 君とは 2 度とキスできない
sinopse:
One day, high school student Shana saved Ai, a boy who jumped into the sea. Since their unprecedented meeting, the two fall in love and kiss one another. But do they know that a secret lies within their unethical love?

(Source: Shogakukan, translated)
